The presenter is starting the programming process for their demonstration. They are about to open a file called "input" which contains the 'Tiny Shakespeare' data set they will use to train a Transformer-based language model. They are using a tool called Google Colab Jupyter to write the code and demonstrate how Chat GPT works, an AI that models the sequence of the English language, which is capable of generating unique responses. They intend to make their own simplified version which replicates Shakespeare's works.